name: The Master Rogue Origami
description:
My entry at @BunnyKnights Master Rogue contest, an origami version of the Master Rogue Bunny #305.

Pixel art based on a painted-black Oriol Esteves's Little Riding Red Hood origami design plus a traditional origami dagger and two rabbit-ear-like folds (not an actual rabbit-ear fold haha).
